\f0\b0 \cf0 \
The Night Hall is both a building -- located in Byenung -- and the council of leaders from the lands and organizations of the Outer Lands (Arq, Runes of Bye, Mobalbesq, Nye Lands).  \
\
It is not unusual for representative or observers from the Krbsh Sea (Krbshana) to attend. The Night Hall building is located right on the Great Lake of Bye and the Hall itself includes two submerged, watery sections, one with fresh water and one with salt water.  Unbeknownst to all but a few, there are occasional representatives from the Remari Islands as well, but the very existence of those islands -- much less the fact of contact with sints and huum from outside of the Enclosure, is a closely-guarded secret.   \
\
From time to time, depending on the topic under discussion -- observers, guests and representatives from other provinces are invited to attend meetings of the Night Hall.\
